{"tid":416582,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[認真post]以前既中學同學做倫敦金","createTime":"2017-09-28T01:38:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-18T15:33:41.000Z","uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9af9a8bc48387c94818a1354114a4e8b5d441f","tid":416582,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:38:12.000Z","msg":"近排撞翻中學同學，同佢都幾friend<br />\n係傾談既過程中知道咗佢近兩三個月開始做倫敦金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n睇得出佢都幾沉醉係揾快錢既過程<br />\n但係睇過高/連登都知道其實倫敦金唔係一個太好既職業，好驚佢越陷越深<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n各位巴打覺得我應該點做?<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n。<br />\n勸下佢退出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n理得佢去死啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跪求大家俾啲意見我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5eaa1aff2f2416e7671b5b3d79ba737cc9eef3e","tid":416582,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:39:47.000Z","msg":"非膠post，派膠死全家"},{"pid":"9f2765dfea813b7329c22a74411c4d5abf6de209","tid":416582,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:41:39.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"053e551cf3a2428bf451ffdc959b979018758b3a","tid":416582,"uid":21423,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d14e67c16459d1c2ab08cabed3f7ad3ec763fb29","tid":416582,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:41:49.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"712591a6eeb085a63d0b2f7e22d4cd3c31f90870","tid":416582,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:42:00.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"fa7aa8f3bb8c4ceebd3dcf83a8bf38fe0a6b0e80","tid":416582,"uid":143131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T01:42:10.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"4739bd8baef3986a2b659643db741d80517071c2